The default memory and disk allocations for tasks are specified by the `cc.default_app_memory` and `cc.default_app_disk_in_mb` properties defined in the BOSH Cloud Controller Worker job. The default log rate limit is specified by the `cc.default_app_log_rate_limit_in_bytes_per_second` property. See [Configuration Properties](https://bosh.io/jobs/cloud_controller_worker?source=github.com/cloudfoundry/capi-release) for more information.
